h visible proof and escalation.\n\n## Concrete product opportunities for WakeTask\n- Adaptive Friction Ladder\n  - Start with low-cognitive wake checks, escalate to movement + scan + timed micro-task if snooze repeats.\n- Reliability-First Alarm Engine UX\n  - Pre-flight check before bedtime (volume route, focus state, permissions, backup trigger readiness) with plain-language pass/fail.\n- Accountability Escalation Graph\n  - If user misses threshold, trigger staged accountability: self-commitment proof -> buddy nudge -> stake event.\n- “No-cheat by design” Missions\n  - Rotation pool with anti-repetition controls, randomization windows, and post-dismiss verification.\n- Critical-Morning Mode\n  - Per-alarm strictness profiles (exam/workflight/day) with harsher dismissal requirements only when needed.\n- Post-wake Outcome Loop\n  - Capture “awake proof” + 3-minute intent task (first action) to convert alarm success into day-start consistency.\n\n## Sources used\n- https://apps.apple.com/us/app/alarmy-alarm-clock-sleep/id1163786766?platform=iphone\n- https://apps.apple.com/us/app/challenges-alarm-clock/id1247289889\n- https://apps.apple.com/us/app/barcode-alarm-clock/id699437630\n- https://apps.apple.com/us/app/barcode-alarm-clock-pro/id731358084\n- https://apps.apple.com/gb/app/nuj-alarm-clock/id1557053396\n- https://apps.apple.com/us/app/walk-me-up-alarm-clock-free/id1022744160\n- https://apps.apple.com/us/app/sleep-cycle-sleep-tracker/id320606217?xs=1\n- local artifact: `.workflow/consumer-radar/data-source-smoke.json`\n- local artifact: `apps/generated-consumer-app-radar/.data/apps.json`\nEOF'","aggregated_output":"","exit_code":0,"status":"completed"}}
